    "import hepi\n",
    "print(hepi.__version__)\n",
    "import smpl\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import hepi.util as util\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import hepi.resummino as rs\n",
    "rs.set_path(\"~/git/resummino_release/\")\n",
    "print (rs.get_path())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c2dda3a7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## aNNLO+NNLL for weakino pair, slepton pair, Z'/W'->leptons,"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "ed7216a4",
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": false
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "skipskipskipskipskipskipskipskipskipskipskipskipskipskipskipRunning: 15 jobs\n",
      "CPU times: user 6.91 s, sys: 1.24 s, total: 8.16 s\n",
      "Wall time: 8.66 s\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x576 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "%%time\n",
    "params = [\n",
    "    \"mastercode_with_gm2.in\",\n",
    "]\n",
    "pss = [    \n",
    "      (1000011,-1000011),\n",
    "     ]\n",
    "\n",
    "for pa,pb in pss:\n",
    "    for param in params:\n",
    "        i = hepi.Input(hepi.Order.aNNLO_PLUS_NNLL,13000,pa,pb,param,\"cteq6l1\",\"cteq66\",1., 1.)\n",
    "        #i = hepi.Input(hepi.Order.LO,13000,pa,pb,param,\"cteq6l1\",\"cteq66\",1., 1.)\n",
    "        li = [i]\n",
    "        li = hepi.mass_scan([i],pa, np.linspace(100,1000,7+8))\n",
    "        rs_dl = rs.run(li,skip=True)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        _,axs = hepi.init_double_plot()\n",
    "        hepi.mass_plot(rs_dl,[\"LO\",\"NLO\",\"aNNLO_PLUS_NNLL\"],pa,axes=axs[0],tight=False)\n",
    "        hepi.mass_plot(rs_dl,[\"K_LO\",\"K_NLO\",\"K_aNNLO_PLUS_NNLL\",\"aNNLO_PLUS_NNLL_OVER_NLO\"],pa, yaxis=None, axes=axs[1],logy=False,tight=False)\n",
    "        hepi.title(axs[0],li[0],scenario=\"mastercode\")"
   ]
  },
